keyFacts: An email notification indicates file sharing activity related to the US v. Maxwell case through the Box platform.
The folder is titled "US v. Maxwell Upload," suggesting it contains materials uploaded for the legal proceedings.
The email originates from the USAfx File Exchange system, which is used for official US government file transfers.
The communication is automated and external, marked as an external email.
The date of the email is June 1, 2021, during the pre-trial phase of the Maxwell case.
